-- Mexico attorney general starts initial probe on Walmex
-- 
-- Thu Apr 26, 2012 3:10pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/04/26/us-mexico-walmart-idUSBRE83P19I20120426

 

 MEXICO CITY  (Reuters) - Mexico's attorney general's office said on Thursday it had begun a preliminary investigation into allegations that the Mexican unit of Wal-Mart Stores Inc ( WMT.N ) ( WALMEXV.MX ) bribed officials to grow its business in the country. 
 (Reporting by Anahi Rama)